texto_en:
Pazzuello is always late, now that he starts working with SUS when it should have been months before, which is why this drastic change is due.
bolsonaro and pazzuello have always denied the severity of the pandemic and have always been against vaccination what happened?
Pazzuello, his presence dishonors your life and that's the end of it.
